      "cookedHtml": "<h2><a name=\"p-140308-transform-your-crm-to-an-agile-crm-in-our-upcoming-webinar-rocket-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-140308-transform-your-crm-to-an-agile-crm-in-our-upcoming-webinar-rocket-1\"></a>Transform your CRM to an agile CRM in our upcoming webinar <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=15\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></h2>\n<h3><a name=\"p-140308-when-wednesday-the-13th-of-september-at-1-pm-aest-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-140308-when-wednesday-the-13th-of-september-at-1-pm-aest-2\"></a>When: Wednesday the 13th of September at 1 pm (AEST)</h3>\n<hr />\n<p>This webinar will deep dive into <strong>how-to’s</strong> for improved productivity, cost-efficiency, reduced admin time, and relationship building.</p>\n<p>Check out what the agenda will look like:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/collision.png?v=15\" title=\":collision:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":collision:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Challenges in delivering world-class customer and employee experience.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/collision.png?v=15\" title=\":collision:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":collision:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Uncover hurdles holding back businesses from delivering key initiatives.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/collision.png?v=15\" title=\":collision:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":collision:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Demonstrate how a flexible relationship management solution can enable speed and agility to market, no matter the industry or use case.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/collision.png?v=15\" title=\":collision:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":collision:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Lessons from customers and how they’ve achieved agility to market</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-140308-sign-up-to-secure-your-spot-herehttpsmondayzoomuswebinarregister8916922430555wn_8rpjwhjdsg